Class Surj' {A B} (R : relation B) (f : A -> B) : Type :=
    {
        surj'_inv : B -> A ;
        surj'_pf: ‚àÄ (b : B), R (f (surj'_inv b)) b
    }.

Record ModelIsomorphism {Œ£ : Signature} (M‚ÇÅ M‚ÇÇ : Model) : Type := mkModelIsomorphism
    {
        mi_f : (Domain M‚ÇÅ) -> (Domain M‚ÇÇ) ;
        mi_inj :> Inj (=) (=) mi_f ;
        mi_surj :> Surj' (=) mi_f ;
        mi_sym : ‚àÄ (s : symbols),
            mi_f <$> (sym_interp M‚ÇÅ s) ‚â° sym_interp M‚ÇÇ s ;
        mi_app : ‚àÄ (x y : Domain M‚ÇÅ),
            mi_f <$> (@app_interp Œ£ M‚ÇÅ x y) ‚â° @app_interp Œ£ M‚ÇÇ (mi_f x) (mi_f y) ;
    }.

Definition isom {Œ£ : Signature} : relation Model :=
    Œª M‚ÇÅ M‚ÇÇ, ‚àÉ (r : ModelIsomorphism M‚ÇÅ M‚ÇÇ), True.

Program Definition ModelIsomorphism_trans {Œ£ : Signature} (M‚ÇÅ M‚ÇÇ M‚ÇÉ : Model)
    (i : ModelIsomorphism M‚ÇÅ M‚ÇÇ)
    (j : ModelIsomorphism M‚ÇÇ M‚ÇÉ)
    : ModelIsomorphism M‚ÇÅ M‚ÇÉ
    :=
    {|
        mi_f := (mi_f j) ‚àò (mi_f i)
    |}.

    apply set_fmap_compose.
Defined.
